<a href="/wiki/The_Tolkien_Society" title="The Tolkien Society">The Tolkien Society</a><sup id="cite_ref-145" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-145" title=""><span>[</span>146<span>]</span></a></sup><br /></td>
