<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFCurry2004">Curry, Patrick (2004). <i>Defending Middle-earth: Tolkien, Myth and Modernity</i>. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/061847885X" class="internal">ISBN 0-618-47885-X</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Defending+Middle-earth%3A+Tolkien%2C+Myth+and+Modernity&amp;rft.aulast=Curry&amp;rft.aufirst=Patrick&amp;rft.au=Curry%2C+Patrick&amp;rft.date=2004&amp;rft.isbn=0-618-47885-X&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:J._R._R._Tolkien"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
