nd_Leaf" title="Tree and Leaf">Tree and Leaf</a></i> (1964)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><i><a href="/wiki/The_Tolkien_Reader" title="The Tolkien Reader">The Tolkien Reader</a></i> (1966)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><i><a href="/wiki/Smith_of_Wootton_Major" title="Smith of Wootton Major">Smith of Wootton Major</a></i> (1967)</span></div>
