eorhtnoth's Death</i> (1953)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><i>Middle English "Losenger": Sketch of an etymological and semantic enquiry</i> (1953)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><i><a href="/wiki/Ancrene_Wisse" title="Ancrene Wisse">Ancrene Wisse</a>: The English Text of the Ancrene Riwle</i> (1962)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><i><a href="/wiki/English_and_Welsh" title="English and Welsh">English and Welsh</a></i> (1963)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap">Introduction to <i><a href="/wiki/Tree_and_Leaf" title="Tree and Leaf">Tree and Leaf</a></i> (1964)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap">Contributions to the <i><a href="/wiki/Jerusalem_Bible" title="Jerusalem Bible">Jerusalem Bible</a></i> (as translator and lexicographer) (1966)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><i>Tolkien on Tolkien</i> (autobiographical) (1966)</span></div>
